WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.985
Cybersecurity is an act of high-impact field.

00:00:02.985 --> 00:00:05.970
It's not enough to just know about cybersecurity,

00:00:05.970 --> 00:00:10.410
you must be able to apply your knowledge to real-world situations.

00:00:10.410 --> 00:00:15.540
The application of cybersecurity principles starts with identifying assets,

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:18.030
which users, machine, software,

00:00:18.030 --> 00:00:20.740
and networks belong to your organization.

00:00:20.740 --> 00:00:23.165
Once you know the assets you must protect,

00:00:23.165 --> 00:00:26.465
the next step is to analyze their vulnerabilities.

00:00:26.465 --> 00:00:28.744
The cyber world can be dangerous,

00:00:28.744 --> 00:00:33.815
you need to identify where an attack might arise and how.

00:00:33.815 --> 00:00:35.735
Armed with this information,

00:00:35.735 --> 00:00:40.175
you can recommend how to secure and protect your organization's assets.

00:00:40.175 --> 00:00:44.570
Lastly, communication is an all important final step.

00:00:44.570 --> 00:00:48.575
Recommendations will only help if decision makers adopt them.

00:00:48.575 --> 00:00:54.630
Your job is to provide a convincing argument for keeping your organization safe.

